Jail Break will give you the experience of real prison life!

Survive from different party forces, only the constant fighting and decrypting clues can help you find the truth!

Come to the Jail Break and show your wisdom and courage, try to find the truth!

Game Features:
◆ This game needs you to use your ingenuity to solve various institutional problems 

◆ Bloody prison fighting, you can only escape if you defeat the enemy;

◆ Smooth movements, giving you a different gaming experience;

◆ A variety of weapons experience, giving you a stimulating combat experience;

◆Diverse skills to enhance your abilities;

Gameplay:
Get clues and hidden items in prison, avoid or defeat enemies, and find ways to escape from prison.

You are welcome to the most mysterious house in the world. A house, that is ready to isolate in its walls anybody who is not able to solve its puzzles. The house of 100 Doors! Mini games, quests, logical  puzzles, hidden objects, jigsaw – all of those you will find on each of 100 rooms of this mysterious house. Find the escape from the room in colourful and well elaborated Egypt, Maya, England and many other locations. It is time to escape the room!
 
Game features:
- Interesting puzzles;
- logical tasks;
- amazing graphics with special attention to details;
- high quality sound;
- help for gamers in official groups and social networks (answers to questions, help in passing the levels);
- constant updates;
-no internal purchases and paid levels: the game and all the updates are for free!
- This game is really complicated! :)
This is a continuation of a popular puzzle 100 Doors Challenge, in which already participated more than four million people in the whole world. 
 
Plunge into the mysterious world of the house of 100 doors.
 
Each new level is a unique puzzle that is becoming more and more complicated. In order to pass a level you have to search for objects, perform tasks, solve conundrums and win in mini games. 
 
Plunge into the mysterious world of the house of 100 doors. 
 
The game 100 doors is a complicated game – it gives food for your brain, just enjoy it!
 
If you have any questions about the game or you just want to communicate with its developers, write a message in our groups in social networks:

★Facebook https://www.facebook.com/proteygames 
 
There is no doubt that a pleasant bonus of this game is the fact that you can play it even if you don’t have internet connection, you can play it even offline.
